Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.55,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Além do tempo, rumo a uma era apaixonante,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.26,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Porque eu acredito que vai mudar...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Embora o presente não possa se mover, esse é o destino, mas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu despertei e não vou desistir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}O entusiasmo que pulsa reflete a era,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Um fogo ardente e lindo.
